<codeline lineno="1"><highlight class="comment">/**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="2"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@file<sp/>event_gnn.dox</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="3"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Detailed<sp/>documentation<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>EventGNN<sp/>Cython<sp/>class,<sp/>a<sp/>specialized<sp/>EventTemplate<sp/>for<sp/>Graph<sp/>Neural<sp/>Network<sp/>(GNN)<sp/>events.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="4"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
