<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>EventGNN_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>specialized<sp/>event<sp/>template<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework,<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>handle<sp/>data<sp/>specific<sp/>to<sp/>Graph<sp/>Neural<sp/>Network<sp/>(GNN)<sp/>applications.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>generic<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>extending<sp/>its<sp/>functionalities<sp/>to<sp/>incorporate<sp/>features<sp/>and<sp/>structures<sp/>relevant<sp/>for<sp/>GNN<sp/>processing.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>event<sp/>object<sp/>tailored<sp/>for<sp/>GNN-based<sp/>analyses.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>EventGNN_class<sp/>The<sp/>EventGNN<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>`EventTemplate`,<sp/>thereby<sp/>gaining<sp/>all<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>event<sp/>indexing,<sp/>weighting,<sp/>and<sp/>tree/branch<sp/>management.<sp/>Its<sp/>primary<sp/>role<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>encapsulate<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`gnn_event`<sp/>object,<sp/>which<sp/>likely<sp/>contains<sp/>specific<sp/>data<sp/>members<sp/>and<sp/>methods<sp/>pertinent<sp/>to<sp/>GNN<sp/>events.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>EventGNN_cinit_dealloc<sp/>Constructors<sp/>and<sp/>Destructors</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>It<sp/>initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`gnn_event`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ev`.<sp/>It<sp/>then<sp/>upcasts<sp/>`self.ev`<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>`event_template*`<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>it<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`,<sp/>allowing<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>treated<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>generic<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>while<sp/>still<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>specialized<sp/>C++<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>standard<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer.<sp/>This<sp/>method<sp/>is<sp/>intentionally<sp/>left<sp/>empty,<sp/>as<sp/>initialization<sp/>logic<sp/>is<sp/>handled<sp/>by<sp/>`__cinit__`<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;destructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>upon<sp/>object<sp/>deallocation.<sp/>It<sp/>deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`gnn_event`<sp/>object<sp/>pointed<sp/>to<sp/>by<sp/>`self.ev`,<sp/>ensuring<sp/>proper<sp/>memory<sp/>management<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>event<sp/>data.<sp/>Note<sp/>that<sp/>`self.ptr`<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>directly<sp/>deleted<sp/>here,<sp/>as<sp/>it<sp/>points<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ev`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>EventGNN_cpp_interaction<sp/>C++<sp/>Interaction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>class<sp/>leverages<sp/>Cython&apos;s<sp/>capabilities<sp/>for<sp/>seamless<sp/>C++<sp/>integration:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class<sp/>EventGNN`:<sp/>Declares<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>gnn_event<sp/>*ev`:<sp/>A<sp/>C++<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>`gnn_event`<sp/>object,<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>C++<sp/>representation<sp/>of<sp/>a<sp/>GNN<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`self.ptr<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;event_template*&gt;(self.ev)`:<sp/>This<sp/>line<sp/>demonstrates<sp/>C++<sp/>upcasting,<sp/>where<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>derived<sp/>class<sp/>(`gnn_event`)<sp/>is<sp/>assigned<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>its<sp/>base<sp/>class<sp/>(`event_template`).<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>to<sp/>fulfill<sp/>the<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>interface<sp/>while<sp/>internally<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>specific<sp/>`gnn_event`<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.event_template<sp/>cimport<sp/>EventTemplate`:<sp/>Imports<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>from<sp/>which<sp/>`EventGNN`<sp/>inherits.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.events.gnn.event_gnn<sp/>cimport<sp/>*`:<sp/>Imports<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`gnn_event`<sp/>class<sp/>declaration<sp/>from<sp/>its<sp/>`.pxd`<sp/>file.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*/</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
